{"tid":2083484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死八婆住我屋企","createTime":"2020-06-28T18:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T10:19:39.000Z","uid":361516,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0e9fa5f4d8676a6b0d3a07d56019608862e99ebe","tid":2083484,"uid":361516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T18:59:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說一月份果時，我細佬話要帶佢條女名叫乜撚<span style=\"color: red;\">張惠敏</span>（讀poly）(電話：61879170)(屌鳩佢唔該)因為佢話佢屋企人政見唔同，佢屋企人藍絲，所以就嚟我哋屋企住先，果時問我細佬住幾耐，話住半年左右，甘咪比佢住住先囉...<br />\n<br />\n過左半年差唔多啦，我再去問我細佬，佢又話六月中走，甘都算啦，點知到左22號，仲係到，然後我細佬又私底下wts我阿妹，話想留佢條女係度。又話乜唔想佢返屋企受佢屋企氣，雖然佢同屋企人都冇乜野...反撚晒囗都算啦，佢見同我地傾唔掂，就已讀不回。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我搵條八婆傾，果時同佢講清楚話比水電費，佢都ok，就比左佢wts我，話以後有水電費就比，我都有問佢住幾耐，佢話住到八月，陪我細佬到九月份開學先走...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我諗左幾日，我wts條八婆話咩住到八月太耐啦，再加上我細佬反口，話條八婆六月中就走。之後條撚樣睇過晒啲message唔覆，cap比我細佬睇。我屌你咩...<br />\n甘撚心機...<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲打點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"421b84a4c850c68b36fb66a4ee77f77aa2b3a1fc","tid":2083484,"uid":337986,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:01:45.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp對話圖都冇張⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f896cc7ca8e4438bf77e86a577a30dbc597fab91","tid":2083484,"uid":337986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"仲有你爸媽唔理架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6928e57c3a43be27a95348ac910f15de57e060de","tid":2083484,"uid":361025,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:03:06.000Z"